## Disable Placement Sway
This mod disables the sway animation when placing buildings, props, and other objects. With this mod, previews will follow the cursor instantly without any springy movement.
This is most noticeable when placing decals.

## Options
- A single toggle in the mod settings to enable or disable the mod

## Compatibility
- Should be compatible with any other mod that doesn't replace the Tools AnimationSystem

Thanks to krzychu124 for guidance on the correct update phase and code review.
